            "stanza_text": "Dans un baiser, l'onde au rivage\nPour consoler la fleur sauvage,\nLe vent du soir conte sa plainte\nLa tourterelle au térébinthe"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Aux flots dormants, quand tout repose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "La lune parle, et dit la cause",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ton dôme blanc, Sainte-Sophie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
