                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Aux flots dormants, quand tout repose,\nLa lune parle, et dit la cause\nTon dôme blanc, Sainte-Sophie,\nEt, tout rêveur, le ciel confie"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Arbre ou tombeau, colombe ou rose,",
